                        Knowledge is power.  In this case power to take your hunting to the next level.  Sound Advice is comprised of
                        videos, articles, and science facts that reveal secrets about deer hearing and how you can leverage this to increase
                        your success.  If you really want to up your game, you really need to check these out!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="text-center" id="NewAdvantageNumbers">3 - Social Media</div>
                    <a href="#AdvantageButtonModal" data-toggle="modal" class=" btn btn-success btn-lg" id="AdvantageButton">
