                        most fun way to interact with us and our great new content on a daily, hourly, and minute by minute basis.  Follow,
                        like, retweet, and share! Get connected, have fun, and please say hi!
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-3">
                    <div class="text-center" id="NewAdvantageNumbers">4 - Featured Articles</div>
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Articles", "Home")" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" id="AdvantageButton">
                        Articles
                    </a>
                    <p class="text-left" id="AdvantageText">
                        Sound Barrier Founder Adam Lewis has numerous articles featured in regional 
                        and national hunting magazines.  If you would like information on where to find 
                        these in-depth articles on the principles of sound concealment, click above.  Check 
                        back often for news of upcoming articles in news stands near you!  
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
